name: testCloseDefaultMultiConfigurationPopOpFromTimeline
description: Verify the ability to close the bubble pop up of Default MultiConfiguration from Timeline
descriptionHtml: Verify the ability to close the bubble pop up of Default MultiConfiguration from Timeline

testStage.description: Verify the ability to close the bubble pop up of Default MultiConfiguration from Timeline

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' on the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click 'Build History' on the side menu
Verify that build bubble pop up is displayed from timeline
